   PATENT RAID: Baker &amp; Botts, a Houston law firm, raided the
Dallas law firm of Baker, Mills &amp; Glast for lawyers
specializing in patent law. Baker &amp; Botts recruited name
partner Jerry W. Mills and as many as 11 associates,
according to E. William Barnett, managing partner of Baker &amp;
Botts. Mr. Mills, 49 years old, will head Baker &amp; Botts's
patent section. Robert A. Baker, managing director of
90-lawyer Baker, Mills, said his law firm has not yet decided
on a new name.
